{"tid":279254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[你真識食.jpg] 杜如風 黃又南宣布「拍拖」","createTime":"2017-06-11T06:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T01:56:25.000Z","uid":5550,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fe449463e9f1bfe9d0c6180349548db4eb5e3a4","tid":279254,"uid":5550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"【東方日報專訊】「旅遊達人」杜如風昨日出席與友人創作的時裝品牌期間限定店開幕，前緋聞男友黃又南現身撐場。她說品牌已成立兩年，一直以網店形式經營，也有意開實體店，奈何租金太貴：「呢間店暫時做一個月，唔使畀租金，如果反應好就唔止一個月，希望做到終老，做租霸。」又南自言經常問對方攞衫，杜如風大爆：「佢大中細碼都話啱身o架！呢啲叫日防夜防家賊難防。」他們由2007年傳緋聞，傳足十年，杜如風戲言兩人今日起正式拍拖，又南會與她的品牌合作推出一系列產品，她笑說：「如果賣得好，就考慮結婚。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%9C%E5%A6%82%E9%A2%A8-%E9%BB%83%E5%8F%88%E5%8D%97%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83-%E6%8B%8D%E6%8B%96-222019219.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259D%259C%25E5%25A6%2582%25E9%25A2%25A8-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%258F%2588%25E5%258D%2597%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583-%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%258B%2596-222019219.html&d=ejsX3kHsxERRDkFiosH%2B%2BP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=bb51527b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%9C%E5%A6%82%E9%A2%A8-%E9%BB%83%E5%8F%88%E5%8D%97%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83-%E6%8B%8D%E6%8B%96-222019219.html</a>"},{"pid":"d3ff675ba133992b4ab7943d5258b5117142bb3b","tid":279254,"uid":34392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:30:32.000Z","msg":"一件排骨  一件肥豬肉 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4131e5b51853e80efb5970ede022e278e7bd5110","tid":279254,"uid":29702,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:34:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d21cc39511f3ed0cb0405b0fa6548e7800c2547f","tid":279254,"uid":29702,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ce1b50efa8a60d14c3e9097c13978915914178a","tid":279254,"uid":29702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11